description: Abel Archer"Armbar"Ht: 6'2"Wt: 185lbsSeason W/L Record (0-0)Jessie Colter"Cut-Throat"Ht: 6'2"Wt: 200lbsSeason W/L Record (2-3) Jessie "Cut-Throat" Colter fought valiantly along side Brock "The Big Show" Avery in their previous tag team match against The Santoros. This week on Naked Kombat, he returns to fight against hot newcomer Abel "Armbar" Archer. Armbar may not have classical training, but he plans on utilizing his long reach to wrap up his opponent and dominate him all the way to the end. Cut-Throat's been working on his conditioning and not to mention he's been here enough times to know how to take control on the mat. Will Armbar come out victorious on his first match or will Cut-Throat improve his record after a ferocious cum covered fuck?
title: Abel "Armbar" Archer vs Jessie "Cut-Throat" Colter
